biography: With a background in particle physics, Philipp Millet has been working as Data Scientist for HotSprings/Umlaut/Accenture in various projects and domains. In 2023 he joined ZEISS Digital Partners as a Machine Learning Engineer. His focus is getting Data Science projects from a PoC stage into production.
